text:
Hey Niteshhh!
You are my first friend of IITK. College ke 1st day hi dosti ho gayi thi apni...2 saal roomie bhi rahi... Ek room me hi baithke FB pe comments me baatein krte the ğŸ¤£... 1st year me to knhi bhi jana hota tha to saath hi jate the... Ghumne bhi hum dono hi nikal jate the... Fresher night ke liye HSS me bhi saath hi gaye the aur phir 2 din pehle hi chhod diya thağŸ˜„. Aero club me bhi bahut enjoy kiya... Tera dedication to kamaal ka tha aero me... Pr tere gusse se dar lagta tha kabhi kabhi ğŸ˜› Swimming bhi seekhne gaye the ek baar, pr bs ek din hi ğŸ˜‚...  Fests me bhi saath jate the.. Kayi baar mera fest me jane ka mann nhi hota tha tab bhi tere "Chal na" ki wajah se jana hi pda aur maja bhi bahut aaya...
